strike.u: FREE GRAB & GO MEAL INFORMATION UPDATE

p.span: We will continue to distribute the free school meals through April 30. If you are already signed up for the meals, there is no need to sign up again. However, if you would like to discontinue the meals or have never signed up, please call Janell Stender at 641-743-6127 or e-mail her at jstender@nodawayvalley.org.

We do ask that if you would like to sign up for the meals or discontinue them, please do so by 8:00 p.m. the night before the delivery. We are busy preparing the meals the day of and are unable to check e-mail that morning. Also, if you need to pick up your meals at a different site than what you signed up for, please call Janell or e-mail by 8:00 p.m. the night before. We are trying to avoid running out of meals in one town and having too many in another. Thanks for your help!
